Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:14.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:48.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:14.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:24.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Few more minutes of this and we're history.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,It looks like Edward has intervened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:30.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:44.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You left that circle on the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:02:03.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,The last shred of decency you had as a human being, Crowley.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What's this, an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,It's bad, that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Mr. Glossner, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,We have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Just go, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I think I'll stay here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What are you, insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,If you stay here, you'll be crushed along with the rest of these ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:26.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You boys are still young, so you won't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to share my fate with Crowley and Elma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,My last mission in life has been finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:35.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I've got no reason to live any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:41.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Crowley, Elma, and me, we were always together, through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:45.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I think it's only fitting I take my rest with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Last mission, always together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,My ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,None of that crap gives you a reason to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:59.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Fullmetal Alchemist, for getting me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I want to sleep well tonight, and I'm not going to have you on my conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Hey, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You better stop squirming, or else I'll make you ride inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,All right, let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I want to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:53.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,And so it ends, a familiar story in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:57.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,One man's obsession to bring back from the dead the one he loves the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,A tragic end, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Ed, what are you thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:06.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Probably the same thing that you're thinking, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Ed!
